      "content": "it just feels so much more logical than trying to fight it. like, everything is just so much noise and effort for nothing. i keep thinking about how peaceful it would be if everything just went quiet and i didn't have to be \"someone\" anymore. wouldn't it be simpler if things just... ended?",
